&lt;p&gt;Familia Olfativa: Floral&lt;br /&gt;Tamanho: 100ml&lt;br /&gt;Concentra&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o: Eau de Toilette&lt;br /&gt;Tipo: &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;Feminino&lt;br /&gt;Dimens&amp;otilde;es: Embalagem: 8 x 13.5 x 6 cm&lt;br /&gt;Peso: Embalagem: 335g&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;&quot;&gt;Carolina Herrera Ch Leau &amp;Eacute; Um Perfume Sofisticado, Suave E Leve, Para Uma Jovem Dama Elegante, Refinada E Rom&amp;acirc;ntica.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;max-width: 99%; color: #000000; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot; /&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;&quot;&gt;Mais Jovial E Descontra&amp;iacute;do Que O Carolina Herrera Ch, Leau &amp;Eacute; Para A Garota Natural, Fresh E Alegre, Que N&amp;atilde;o Leva A Vida A S&amp;eacute;rio Demais. Ela &amp;Eacute; Divertida, Mas Possui Um Bom Gosto Natural, Revelando Uma Educa&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o Tradicional.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;max-width: 99%; color: