&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #3a3d41; font-family: &#039;Open Sans&#039;, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;&quot;&gt;Ch Priv&amp;eacute;e &amp;eacute; um Perfume Carolina Herrera Feminino oriental floral. &amp;Eacute; sensual e sofisticado. Um perfume que captura a feminilidade enigm&amp;aacute;tica da mulher. Ch Priv&amp;eacute;e Carolina Herrera surpreende por sua fragr&amp;acirc;ncia que combina ousadia e sensualidade com notas de Osmanthus, Pimenta-Rosa, Alm&amp;iacute;scar e Baunilha, enla&amp;ccedil;ados pela sensualidade do Couro. Elaborado pelo perfumista Dominique Ropion, Ch Priv&amp;eacute;e Carolina Herrera retrata a aud&amp;aacute;cia e eleg&amp;acirc;ncia da mulher moderna.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;max-width: 99%; color: #000000; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-st