&lt;div class=&quot;container&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;tab-content&quot;&gt;
&lt;section id=&quot;tab2&quot; class=&quot;tab-pane page-product-box active&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;rte&quot;&gt;Topo: Cardamomo e c&amp;iacute;tricos Cora&amp;ccedil;ao: Rosa e l&amp;iacute;rio Fundo: Ol&amp;iacute;bano e madeira de cashmere&lt;/div&gt;
